E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('887','7','嘉鱼政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2011]29</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">川气东送是国家重点天然气工程。川气东送嘉鱼段天然气管道工程经潘湾、新街、官桥等三个镇，工程战线长、任务大、涉及临时用地范围广。为确保工程顺利实施，根据《中华人民共和国土地管理法》、《湖北省土地管理实施办法》、《省人民政府公布湖北省征地统一年产值标准和区片综合地价的通知》（鄂政发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2009]46</span>号）等有关规定，参照省内周边城市的补偿标准和办法，结合我县实际，现将天然气工程项目临时用地和拆迁补偿标准通知如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、临时用地补偿标准<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">临时用地土地补偿费按照综合地类每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩包干（不足一年按一年计）。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、临时使用非农建设用地、荒地、未利用地原则上不予补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">经核实，确有开荒利用且权属明晰的，对土地所有权人或使用人按每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩进行补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、临时使用耕地、园地、养殖水面等其它农用地一年以内的，按以下标准补偿：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、青苗补偿（施工时间有农作物）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①水稻：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②茶叶、苎麻、药材：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③芝麻、花生：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④小麦、油菜：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤甘蔗：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑥豆类：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">600</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑦草籽：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑧红薯：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑨棉花类：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1200</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑩芦（竹）笋：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4500</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、蔬菜类<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2200</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩（精细大棚蔬菜<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4600</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、果树及其他类<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①樟树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②挂果桔树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③挂果果树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵，果苗<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10-20</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④新建竹园<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">540</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩，生长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>年以上竹林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1300</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤防护林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1700</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩，用树林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">900</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；经济林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">700</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩，特殊用途林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">900</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩，新炭林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">900</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩，杂灌木丛、柴草山<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、树木类<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）常绿树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5cm</span>以下<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5-8cm20</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9-12cm36</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13-16cm52</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17cm</span>以上<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">68</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）落叶树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5cm</span>以上<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5-8cm20</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9-12cm36</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13-16cm52</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17cm</span>以上<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">65</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>棵。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）上述树木直径均以地面高<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.2</span>米处为准。直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5cm</span>以下成片绿树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1280</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩，落叶树<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1120</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；对自然生长直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5cm</span>以上的树木，在此标准基础上，下浮<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50%</span>进行补偿；对特殊树种按当年有关部门发布的市场价格的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30%</span>补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、苗圃和花卉类<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">根据实际情况，按照相关文件规定进行补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、养殖水面等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①精养鱼池<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②一般鱼池<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③自然湖面<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">350</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④苗种池<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤藕塘、藕田<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1100</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑥龙虾（鳖、鳝）池<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9000</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、其他有关项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①水泥杆<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10-12m1500</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>根，光缆杆<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10-12m1500</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>根；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②宅基地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1200/</span>平方米；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③水泥地平、围墙<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>平方米；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④简易砖木房屋结构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>平方米。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">四、地面附着物及其它有关设施补偿标准<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">房屋拆迁补偿按照市场评估价给予补偿，其它地面附着物（粪窖、猪圈、牛棚、厕所、水井、大棚）以及其它有关设施（护坡、围墙、明沟、地坪、乡村道路等）的补偿，除坟墓按<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span>座补偿外，其它根据实际情况，按市场评估价等相关规定进行补偿。同时，由该项目业主与村组（农户）签订《拆迁补偿协议书》。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">五、补偿方式及相关要求<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）补偿方式。由县协调领导小组和该项目业主会同镇村组指定负责人、物权人三方一起进行土地实地丈量，根据实际量地面积和统一的标准进行补偿费核算。经登记造册后，由县协调领导小组直接拨付补偿款到镇财经所或村委会。在项目业主的监督下，由村委会支付补偿给实物权属人，经物权人签字确认，并及时对外公示。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">农村集体经济组织负责人将补偿费支付给涉及农户，各级不得侵占、克扣、截留和挪用临时用地补偿费，县政府将组织纪检监察、国土、财政、经管、农业等部门对临时用地补偿费落实情况进行专项检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）施工临时用地补偿费支付前，由该项目业主与村委会签订《临时用地补偿协议》，同时项目业主与国土部门需办理工程施工土地复垦保证金协议，确保后期土地正常耕种。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）沿线各级和有关部门要切实加强领导，积极做好国家重点工程项目建设用地补偿工程，安排好沿线群众的生产生活，确保管道工程建设的顺利实施。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）在临时用地或拆迁中，如遇到土地权属争议，由县协调领导小组会同土地行政主管部门、镇村组织争议双方协商解决；协商不成的，由县人民政府裁决，不得影响工程的正常施工。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）对于在临时用地范围内突击建设的建筑物、突击栽种的树林一律不予补偿，并依法强制清除。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）对于已按补偿标准给予补偿而租用土地的所有者或使用者拒不在《临时用地补偿协议书》或《拆迁补偿协议书》上签字、盖章或拒不搬迁的，建议方可以依法申请人民法院强制执行，以保证国家重点建设项目顺利进行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（七）对于煽动群众闹事、阻挠管道工程建设征地、临时租用地和拆迁工作，造成恶劣后果的，其首要分子，由公安机关依照《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚条例》的有关规定予以处理；对触犯刑律、构成犯罪的，由司法机关依法追究其刑事责任。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（八）涉及公路、水利、林业、电力、通讯等设施建设的，按照相关部门的规定处理。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 33.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 245pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 17.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span>一一年三月二十日<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('888','282','admin','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">嘉鱼古名沙阳堡。西晋太康元年（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">280</span>）置沙阳县，属武昌郡。南朝齐建元元年（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">478</span>）省县入江夏郡，南朝陈永定元年（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">557</span>）复置，属上隽郡。隋开皇九年（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">589</span>）并入蒲圻县，以沙阳县地置鲇渎镇。南唐升元元年（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">937</span>）改镇为场（市），保大十一年（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">953</span>）升场为嘉鱼县，因取《诗经&middot;小雅&middot;南有嘉鱼》之义而得名，属鄂州，元属武昌路、明清属武昌府，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1913</span>年属江汉道，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1916</span>年属省，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1932</span>年属第一行政督察区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">1949</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">年属沔阳专区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1951</span>年属大冶专区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1952</span>年属孝感专区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1959</span>年属武汉市。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1960</span>年并入武昌县。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1961</span>年复置，属孝感专区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1965</span>年后属咸宁专区、地区，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1998</span>年属地级咸宁市。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">1997</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">年，嘉鱼县面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1017</span>平方千米，人口<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">33.8</span>万，辖<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>乡：鱼岳镇、潘家湾镇、渡普镇、高铁岭镇、官桥镇、老官咀镇、陆溪镇、州镇、舒桥镇、新街镇、八斗乡、合镇乡、虎山乡、烟墩乡、朱砂乡。县府驻鱼岳镇。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">2000</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">年第五次人口普查，全县总人口<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">358646</span>人，其中（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>个镇、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>个乡）：陆溪镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18257</span>人，高铁岭镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18855</span>人，舒桥镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13965</span>人，官桥镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11921</span>人，鱼岳镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">94297</span>人，新街镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26919</span>人，潘家湾镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">36277</span>人，渡普镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16423</span>人，老官嘴镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19792</span>人，牌洲湾镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">55533</span>人，虎山乡<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8026</span>人，八斗乡<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13093</span>人，朱砂乡<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11176</span>人，烟墩乡<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14112</span>人。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">2004</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">年底，嘉鱼县总人口<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">363581</span>人。辖<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个镇，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>个居委会、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">82</span>个村委会。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">截至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2009</span>年底，嘉鱼县辖<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个镇。共有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>个居委会、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">82</span>个村委会。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('889','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 29.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2011]116</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 29.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">为做好城市规划区内征地拆迁补偿安置工作，处理好国家、集体、个人三者利益，促进城市建设发展，根据国家相关法律法规规定，结合我县实际，对城市规划区内征地拆迁补偿标准进行了调整，并就做好安置工作作出了原则规定。现就有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、本通知所称的城市规划区，是指城市建成区以及因城市建设和发展需要，必须实行规划控制的区域。规划区的具体范围由县政府在编制的城市建设规划、工业园区规划以及旅游景区规划中，根据城乡经济社会发展水平和统筹城乡发展的需要来划定。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、征地拆迁补偿安置工作必须依法、合法。严格遵照《中华人民共和国城市规划法》、《中华人民共和国土地管理法》和国务院《国有土地上房屋征收与补偿条例》精神执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、我县城市规划区内征地拆迁补偿安置标准应统一，必须严格按政策标准执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">四、未经审批建设的违法违规建筑，以及征地及拆迁公告发布后，抢建、抢种的房屋及附着物、树木，不予补偿，并依法予以拆除。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">五、已经分步实施拆迁的地段，同一规划红线范围内区位基准价已经评估确认的被拆迁房屋，按照同一地段、同一补偿标准的原则执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">六、涉及国家重点基础设施项目工作的征地拆迁补偿，按国家有关规定执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">七、县国有土地房屋征收与补偿办公室要加强对城市规划区内征地拆迁补偿安置工作的指导管理监督，负责审核拆迁补偿安置实施方案；负责补偿安置资金的监督使用；负责协调处理房屋征收、补偿和搬迁纠纷；负责拆迁补偿安置的档案管理工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">八、城市规划区征地拆迁还建安置必须按照&ldquo;统一规划、集中安置&rdquo;的原则进行。县规划执法局要根据城市建设和工业园区发展做好拆迁还建点规划。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">九、全县城市规划区内建设项目的征地补偿，按《省人民政府关于公布征地统一年产值标准及区片综合地价的通知》（鄂政发〔<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2009</span>〕<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">46</span>号）标准执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">十、城市规划区范围内建设项目涉及集体土地上房屋及附着物拆迁的，根据其结构、等级系数以及新旧程度等评估结果计算补偿，具体标准见附件二、附件三。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">十一、涉及林木砍伐的，按下列标准进行补偿：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）果树补偿：成林挂果树每棵<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">120</span>元，半挂果树每棵<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>元，非成林挂果树每棵<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>元，当年新栽的按苗木成本补偿，但苗木数量不得超过林业部门规定的正常行直株间距标准。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）用材林按每株胸径大小予以补偿，地上<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">120</span>公分处胸径大于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>公分的成材林每株补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>元，小于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>公分的幼树每株补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>元，株高<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>～<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">120</span>公分的幼树每株补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）楠竹每株补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）房前屋后成林杂木按每棵<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>元补偿，成片田地树苗按每亩<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1200</span>元进行补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）其它自然生长的次生林不予补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">十二、拆迁房屋内设施及地面附属物按下列标准进行补偿：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）灶。砖砌双烟双灶每个<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>元，其他型灶每个<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）水井。深<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>米以下的每口补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>元，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>米至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>米的每口补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>元，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>米以上的每口补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）地坪及晒坪。已硬化的每平方米补偿<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">35</span>元，未硬化的不予补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 6pt 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-para-margin-right: 6.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: .57gd; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）农村粪池。按其容积计算，砖石结构的每立方补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">140</span>元，其他结构的每立方米补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70</span>元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 6pt 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-para-margin-right: 6.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: .57gd; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）沼汽池。已享受政府或部门补贴的，按每立方米<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">450</span>元进行补偿；未享受政府或部门补贴的，按每立方米<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">520</span>元进行补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 6pt 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-para-margin-right: 6.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: .57gd; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）水电补偿费。包括安装费、材料费等，每户补<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>元。有水无电的、有电无水的减半补偿；水电设施均无的不予补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Calibri\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">十三、其他补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）房屋搬迁补助费。包括拆迁户的拆迁劳力费、运输费、误工损失费等，每户补助<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）住房临时安置补助费。实行货币补偿的，按每月每平方米补助<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.5</span>元；实行产权调换的，按协议约定的期限每月每平方米补助<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.5</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）坟墓。三年内（含三年）新坟每座<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>元，三年以上旧坟每座<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">十四、各镇的征地拆迁补偿安置工作参照本通知执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">十五、本通知自印发之日起执行，并根据实际情况适时进行调整。《县人民政府办公室关于调整县城规划区建设拆迁补偿标准的通知》（嘉政办发〔<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2003</span>〕<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">23</span>号）同时废止。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\">一一年十<st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"9\\\\\" month=\\\\\"1\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\">一月九<span style=\\\\\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1531','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-27/665309581e4cff71d54456bef1706e2c.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n县长余珂讲话<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">26</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，陆溪镇藕塘村人头攒动，锣鼓喧天。我县&ldquo;联创齐争&rdquo;共同推进国土整治惠民项目开工典礼在这里隆重举行。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">省国土资源厅党组成员陈新华、市国土资源局副局长严新道、县长余珂、县人大副主任李电波、副县长李德炳、县政协副主席刘平出席开工典礼。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">陈新华指出，嘉鱼县开展&ldquo;联创齐争&rdquo;共同推进国土整治惠民项目活动，是贯彻中央关于深入开展创先争优活动的纵向延伸，是落实部省&ldquo;联创齐争&rdquo;座谈会精神的务实举措，是在土地整治项目建设中转变工作方式、提升服务效能的具体行动。他希望嘉鱼县以此为契机，充分调动各方积极性和创造性，进一步加强沟通与交流，做到设计好、质量好、效应好&ldquo;三个好&rdquo;，真正把这个项目建设成惠民工程、德政工程。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂对出席开工仪式的各级领导表示热烈欢迎。他说，举办&ldquo;联创齐争&rdquo;活动，旨在打造土地整治的惠民工程、精品工程，进一步改善全县农业生产条件，促进城乡统筹发展，加速&ldquo;湖北经济强县、长江临港新城&rdquo;建设进程。他要求相关部门认真抓好项目施工和建设工作，以保障民生为落脚点，确保按期完成建设任务，把项目建成全市土地整理的精品工程和全省的示范工程。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">陆溪镇藕塘村土地整理项目是省级投资重点建设项目，该项目涉及藕塘村、邱家湾村、花园村、官洲村</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个村，总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，整理土地</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"公顷\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"533\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">533</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">公顷</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。项目的建设，对进一步加强耕地保护，提高土地利用水平，增强农业综合生产能力，推进农业产业化必将起到积极的示范作用。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">陆溪镇党委书记华红、镇长周素琴参加开工仪式。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-27/a4e71776f9d7b9e24e20dbc0a60730a4.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n项目开工现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</d